      <li class="toplevel"><a data-list-item href="workflow.html#step5"
          >Step 5. Build your WebApp when you build the android app</a>
          <ol class="toc">
              <li><a data-list-item href="workflow.html#copywebapp"
                     >task copyWebApplication</a>
              </li>
              <li><a data-list-item href="workflow.html#deletewebapp"
                     >task deleteWebApplication</a>
              </li>
              <li><a data-list-item href="workflow.html#dependson"
                     >copyWebApplication.dependsOn</a>
              </li>
              <li><a data-list-item href="workflow.html#applicationvariants"
                     >android.applicationVariants.all</a>
              </li>
          </ol>
      </li>
